			<h4><a id="comment_link_26216275" name="comment_link_26216275" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=1071869&amp;cid=26216275" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(26216275)">Some tech books I enjoyed a lot</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_26216275" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 26216275); return false">Score:4</a>, Informative)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~stsp">stsp <span class="uid">(979375)</span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
