	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_26216275"><ul>
<li>
<i>Thinking in C++</i> by Bruce Eckel <a href="http://mindview.net/Books/TICPP/ThinkingInCPP2e.html" title="mindview.net">http://mindview.net/Books/TICPP/ThinkingInCPP2e.html</a> [mindview.net]
</li><li>
<i>Computer Networks</i> by Andrew Tanenbaum <a href="http://www.prenhall.com/tanenbaum/details2.html" title="prenhall.com">http://www.prenhall.com/tanenbaum/details2.html</a> [prenhall.com]
</li><li>
<i>Structured Computer Organization</i> by Andrew Tanenbaum <a href="http://www.pearsonhighered.com/educator/academic/product/0,,0131485210,00%2Ben-USS_01DBC.html" title="pearsonhighered.com">http://www.pearsonhighered.com/educator/academic/product/0,,0131485210,00%2Ben-USS_01DBC.html</a> [pearsonhighered.com]
