</li><li>
<i>Design and Implementation of the FreeBSD Operating System</i> by Marshall Kirk McKusick and George V. Neville-Neil <a href="http://www.mckusick.com/books.html" title="mckusick.com">http://www.mckusick.com/books.html</a> [mckusick.com]
</li><li>
<i>Code Quality</i> by Diomidis Spinellis <a href="http://www.spinellis.gr/codequality/" title="spinellis.gr">http://www.spinellis.gr/codequality/</a> [spinellis.gr]
</li></ul></div>
